{
  "message": "refactor(dashboard): add mobile-responsive layout system\n\nCreate a composable layout system with shared partials:\n- _head.html: shared <head> element with scripts\n- _header.html: top bar with hamburger menu for mobile\n- _mobile_backdrop.html: overlay for mobile sidebar\n- _mobile_nav.html: bottom navigation bar for mobile\n- _layout_start.html / _layout_end.html: wrapper partials\n\nUpdate _sidebar.html with responsive behavior:\n- x-show/x-transition for slide-in/out animation\n- Fixed positioning on mobile, static on desktop\n- Click-away handler to close on mobile\n\nRefactor all secondary pages to use layout system:\n- activity.html, settings.html, resources.html, error.html\n\nAdd mobile support to vm_detail.html manually (extra scripts).\n\nAll pages now have consistent mobile UX with hamburger menu,\nslide-out sidebar, backdrop overlay, and bottom navigation.\n\n\ud83e\udd16 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
  "files": [
    {
      "sha": "5c0217045297c671bbdbbd75e50ec30e12fd3127",
      "filename": "pkg/dashboard/templates/_head.html",
      "status": "added",
